      <title>克里姆林宫就洪水表示：最困难的日子还在后面</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-floods-most-difficult-days-are-still-ahead-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫周二表示，总统弗拉基米尔·普京的重点是应对洪水，但库尔干和秋明地区最困难的日子还在后面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-floods-most-difficult-days-are-still-ahead-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:32:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行加速中国财富扩张，有望实现招聘目标</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-accelerate-china-wealth-expansion-track-meet-hiring-target-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行全球财富主管表示，尽管面临经济逆风，汇丰银行仍计划加速在中国扩张财富业务，并有望在明年将其员工人数增加近一倍，同时推进其亚洲支点战略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-accelerate-china-wealth-expansion-track-meet-hiring-target-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国房地产部称今年泰国房地产增长超过 4%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-sees-more-than-4-growth-this-year-property-measures-ministry-says-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国财政部表示，随着政府试图重振经济活动，在周二批准的提振房地产业措施的推动下，泰国经济今年预计将增长 4% 以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-sees-more-than-4-growth-this-year-property-measures-ministry-says-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:08:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜媒体在选举前夕刺伤韩国总统</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-media-takes-stab-souths-president-eve-elections-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜国家控制的媒体在选举前一天称其邻国韩国总统尹锡烈为“法西斯独裁者”和“战争贩子”，该选举将决定目前由尹的反对者主导的议会组成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-media-takes-stab-souths-president-eve-elections-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 07:42:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中共中央政治局委员赵立坚率代表团访问朝鲜</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-communist-party-politburo-member-zhao-lead-delegation-north-korea-kcna-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据朝鲜官方通讯社朝中社周二报道，由最高立法委员、党的三号官员赵乐际率领的中国政府和共产党代表团将对朝鲜进行正式友好访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-communist-party-politburo-member-zhao-lead-delegation-north-korea-kcna-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 07:20:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾抗议者践踏习近平肖像，谴责中国海上“侵略”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-protesters-trample-xi-effigy-condemn-chinas-maritime-aggression-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，马尼拉的抗议者践踏中国国家主席习近平的肖像，谴责中国在南海“侵略”菲律宾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-protesters-trample-xi-effigy-condemn-chinas-maritime-aggression-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚报告限制社交媒体内容的请求增加</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/malaysia-reports-increase-requests-restrict-social-media-content-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚周二表示，敦促 Facebook 运营商 Meta 和短视频服务 TikTok 加强对其平台的监控，政府报告今年有害社交媒体内容急剧增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/malaysia-reports-increase-requests-restrict-social-media-content-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:09:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国将在人工智能领域投资 70 亿美元，以保持芯片优势</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/south-korea-invest-7-bln-ai-bid-retain-edge-chips-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈周二表示，韩国将在 2027 年之前在人工智能领域投资 9.4 万亿韩元（69.4 亿美元），作为保持尖端半导体芯片全球领先地位的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/south-korea-invest-7-bln-ai-bid-retain-edge-chips-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梵蒂冈外长对越南进行史无前例的访问</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/vatican-foreign-minister-travels-vietnam-unprecedented-visit-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梵蒂冈外交部长保罗·理查德·加拉格尔周二开始对共产党统治的越南进行史无前例的为期六天的访问，双方致力于建立更密切的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/vatican-foreign-minister-travels-vietnam-unprecedented-visit-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾军演模拟击退中国演习演变成攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-war-games-simulate-repelling-chinese-drill-that-turns-into-attack-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾国防部周二表示，今年台湾的年度军演将在海上进行“杀伤区”演习，以打破封锁，并模拟中国突然将其环岛常规演习转变为实际攻击的场景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-war-games-simulate-repelling-chinese-drill-that-turns-into-attack-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:14:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
